@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lwnspw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.59 / tmp + 0.31)) / (wp.cos(v1 + 0.45) * (v2 + 0.70 + tmp + 0.58)))
    v2 = (0.94 * 0.65)
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.69) - ((tmp + 0.41 + v0 + 0.64) + wp.sin(v2 + 1.00)))
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.cos(v1 + 0.84) + (v1 + 0.68 - tmp + 0.95)))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = (0.29 + wp.abs((v1 + 0.31 * v2 + 0.62)))
    data[tid] = v0
